        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-239844ed-f62f-4381-8e98-a04bdc46ad03">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-239844ed-f62f-4381-8e98-a04bdc46ad03">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-239844ed-f62f-4381-8e98-a04bdc46ad03" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-11-27/debates/9f132463-9ab4-4f71-b2f0-9d751fb4dbcb/AtomicEnergy(BritishScientistsAchievements)#contribution-239844ed-f62f-4381-8e98-a04bdc46ad03">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">A White Paper was issued by the late Government in 1945. I might have a lot to say on these matters and I dare say that some day another White Paper will be published giving a fuller account of what happened in 1945 and earlier. But I do not think that the time has come yet.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-239844ed-f62f-4381-8e98-a04bdc46ad03" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-11-27/debates/9f132463-9ab4-4f71-b2f0-9d751fb4dbcb/AtomicEnergy(BritishScientistsAchievements)#contribution-239844ed-f62f-4381-8e98-a04bdc46ad03">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-de443c64-7e78-4097-97c9-b51fdd575eba">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-de443c64-7e78-4097-97c9-b51fdd575eba">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-de443c64-7e78-4097-97c9-b51fdd575eba">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-de443c64-7e78-4097-97c9-b51fdd575eba">
                Mr. Smith
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-de443c64-7e78-4097-97c9-b51fdd575eba" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-11-27/debates/9f132463-9ab4-4f71-b2f0-9d751fb4dbcb/AtomicEnergy(BritishScientistsAchievements)#contribution-de443c64-7e78-4097-97c9-b51fdd575eba">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the Prime Minister bear in mind that it is my desire to put on record credit where it is due, particularly to those men who worked so long and so hard, like Professors Rutherford, Chatwick and Cockcroft and Dr. Allibone? In some parts of the world that credit does not seem to be given to these men. Will the right hon. Gentleman bear in mind, when preparing his statement, that, if I remember rightly, the last White Paper was published before the termination of hostilities and could not contain the information for which I am asking? Will the Prime Minister remember this, so that the whole facts can be placed before the public and the world can see, as the years go by, what they owe to British engineers?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-de443c64-7e78-4097-97c9-b51fdd575eba" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-11-27/debates/9f132463-9ab4-4f71-b2f0-9d751fb4dbcb/AtomicEnergy(BritishScientistsAchievements)#contribution-de443c64-7e78-4097-97c9-b51fdd575eba">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-9f59ef26-ff57-4f96-a2c7-1859d23770dc">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-9f59ef26-ff57-4f96-a2c7-1859d23770dc">
