        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-9f59ef26-ff57-4f96-a2c7-1859d23770dc">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-9f59ef26-ff57-4f96-a2c7-1859d23770dc">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9f59ef26-ff57-4f96-a2c7-1859d23770dc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-11-27/debates/9f132463-9ab4-4f71-b2f0-9d751fb4dbcb/AtomicEnergy(BritishScientistsAchievements)#contribution-9f59ef26-ff57-4f96-a2c7-1859d23770dc">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Yes, Sir. No one would be more content than myself to see the whole story unfolded. I <span id="616" class="column-number" data-column-number="616"></span> pressed this matter several times since the war, during the period when previous Governments were in power. But I do not think at this particular moment I could add anything to what I have said in my answer.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9f59ef26-ff57-4f96-a2c7-1859d23770dc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
