<p class="">Is the House to understand from the right hon. Gentleman's original answer that he does not think the time is opportune to give anything more than the meagre information that so far has been disclosed about our efforts in furthering atomic energy? Will he say whether this matter is a closed subject because of military security?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
