                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f65a8bf0-f064-4223-bc1a-f39e51944352" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-11-27/debates/9f132463-9ab4-4f71-b2f0-9d751fb4dbcb/AtomicEnergy(BritishScientistsAchievements)#contribution-f65a8bf0-f064-4223-bc1a-f39e51944352">
